b"The COVID-19 pandemic affects us all. But it has hit the most vulnerable among us the hardest. Food banks play a vital role in serving these populations in Canada and with greater demand in times like these, even as we stay apart, we've got to support each other.

That's why we at MCCAIN Foods are donating up to 20 million pounds of potatoes to food banks across the country, including Second Harvest and Food Banks Canada.

That's 60 million servings provided to Canadians currently in need.

Every day, families gather around the dinner table. We are proud to play a part in that sense of community and belonging.

Because now, more than ever, we're all in this together.

#SuperTogether
